  <brief_title>Effect of Sodium Bicarbonate Buccal Infiltration on the Success of Inferior Alveolar Nerve Block</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Sodium Bicarbonate Buccal Infiltration on the Success of Inferior Alveolar Nerve Block in the Mandibular First Molar With Symptomatic Irreversible Pulpitis: a Prospective, Randomized Double-blind Study</official_title>
